_sText:
Im submitting my remake of zm_deep_thought on behalf of the original creator. My clan server loved the original, and asked me to redo it to make it even better. So I put some time into it, came up with ideas, and got them into the map.

----------------------------

Slots: 40

--------------

Changelog/Fix:

- Fixed rooms.
- Added more props.
- Added Better lighting.
- Added more Decals.
- Retextured areas.
- Bumped the Fps up.
- Added mini-secret weapon area, with teleport.
- Added flickering lights.
- Added Cubemaps.
--------------------------------------------

Enjoy my remake, of this classic, and wonderful zombie mod map.
